  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to say a prayer to petition your deity for&nbsp;their divine blessing. Choose 1 of the prayers listed below.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Each prayer has a listed <strong>MP</strong> cost that you must spend when&nbsp;you say your prayer.</p>\n<p>You can only have 1 prayer active at a time. If you say another prayer while you already have a prayer active, the first prayer immediately ends without granting any benefit.</p>\n<p>Once during the next minute, you can apply the prayer benefit&nbsp;to a Spell you cast. If your Spell targets more than 1 creature,&nbsp;your prayer only benefits 1 of the targets (your choice).</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.Chy4mrMHU88SLeJH]{Prayer of Destruction}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.1PaPdN0pzt6TZ3J8]{Prayer of Guidance}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.k9YeuyL9vA1VqJCn]{Prayer of Restoration}</p>\n<p><strong>Unused Blessing:</strong> If the prayer ends without granting any&nbsp;benefit, you regain the <strong>MP</strong> spent to say the prayer.</p>",
